<title>USA: Illinois direct hogs steady/off $0.50 - USDA.</title>
<headline>Illinois direct hogs steady/off $0.50 - USDA.</headline>
<dateline>SPRINGFIELD 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>USDA said barrows and gilts</p>
<p>steady to $0.50 lower. Demand was moderate. Top $57.50 per</p>
<p>cwt.</p>
<p>US 1-2 230-260 lbs. 56.00-57.00, some 57.50, few 55.50</p>
<p>Sows - steady/weak. Top $53.00.</p>
<p>    US 1-3   300-400 lbs. 43.00-46.00</p>
<p>		 400-500 lbs. 45.00-48.00</p>
<p>		 500-600 lbs. 48.00-50.00, few 51.00</p>
<p>few over 600 lbs. 50.00-52.00, few 53.00</p>
</text>
